# My build of dmenu

This is my build of dmenu, with the following patches added:
 - dmenu-highlight-20201211-fcdc159.diff
 - dmenu-scroll-20180607-a314412.diff
 - dmenu-xresources-alt-5.0.diff

Also added is emoji support. Use `libxft-bgra-git` from the AUR, until
the pull request in question is merged, otherwise dmenu will crash.

dmenu - dynamic menu
====================
dmenu is an efficient dynamic menu for X.


Requirements
------------
In order to build dmenu you need the Xlib header files.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (dmenu is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install dmenu
(if necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running dmenu
-------------
See the man page for details.
